step1:- In jenkins install the maven plugin
Name of the plugin "PipelineMavenIntegration"

step2:- Install Maven package in the Jenkins Linux server
https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi
Download Maven tarball and unpack it

step3: Configure Maven home in Jenkins "configureTools"
Mention the home dir of maven "/opt/apache-maven-3.9.1"

step4:- IN jenkins Create a new Maven Job
- Mention the git repository
- In Buid section 
        - Root POM : pom.xml
        - Goals and options :- clean install
        
 step5: Trigger build
